_sText: Surf_Vanilla_Beta2 Map by: Apexi Skybox by KarateKafer Letters by Chrazini ========================== Questions? Comments? Email me at daninator007@gmail.com or add me to steam daninator007 ========================== This is my newest map. Surf_Vanilla. It was supposed to be a remake of my very first surf map but it looked cool so i doubled it and this is how it turned out. I am posting this because people have been anxious to play this. Do not be upset if you find and glitches and what not. ========================== *Please not that sometimes ramp textures might disappear or turn black. This issue is trying to be resolved. Do not complain about it please. This issue will eventually be fixed in the beta3 or final.* ///Special Features: Buyzone At top of the map. Bombsite is activated 1 minute after game starts. Surf ramps can be surfed in any direction.\\\ ========================== Guns:mp5, ump45, m4a1, ak47, m3, auto shotgun, deagle, p228, knife, Anything you can buy ========================== Installation: Put into your cstrike/maps folder. ========================== Do not rate this map bad because you don't like it or something about it. ========================== Thanks to all that tested this map. Made Suggestions and helped in anyway with it. ========================== Enjoy Brought to you by Gamerline Studio
